.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, cranberry, cucumber, mango
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, collecting, fishing, gardening
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, dubstep, funk, electronic
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the person eating cherry is on the left of the fan of funk##1
3. the person eating cherry is on the right of the fan of house##1
4. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the fan of funk##2
6. the person eating cranberry is between the person eating cherry and the person eating cucumber##2
7. the fan of house is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food    | cucumber | cranberry  | cherry | mango      |
| Hobby   | fishing  | gardening  | baking | collecting |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | house | dubstep | funk     |

