1. the person who's sport is volleyball is the fan of disco##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is the fan of country##1
3. the fan of reggae is on the far left##1
4. the fan of blues is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
5. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
6. the person eating papaya is between the fan of disco and the fan of reggae##2
7. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Food          | pepper  | papaya    | pomegranate | lettuce  |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | blues       | disco        | country    |
| Sport         | cycling | badminton | volleyball  | handball |

