3. the person eating orange is between the person eating lettuce and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far right##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
7. the person watching time-travel movies is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
8. the person watching adventure movies is the person eating pomegranate##1

