3. the person eating lime is between the person eating zucchini and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left##1
5. the person eating lime is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
6. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
7. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food   | kale | zucchini     | lime | cucumber       |
| Hobby      | sudoku  | traveling | card-games  | gardening |
| Pet        | turtle  | goat      | pony        | bird      |

