City: new-york, venice, miami, paris
1. the person watching disaster movies is the person traveling to paris##1
2. the person traveling to miami is the mechanic##1
3. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the dancer##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
5. the person traveling to venice is between the person watching romance movies and the mechanic##2
6. the person traveling to paris is on the far right##1
7. the person traveling to venice is the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
