There 4 different types of food: onion, mango, grapes, pineapple
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, funk, rock, soul
There are 4 different nationalities: german, indian, italian, mexican
1. the fan of country is the person eating mango##1
2. the person eating onion is between the person eating grapes and the indian##2
3. the person eating grapes is the fan of funk##1
4. the person eating grapes is between the fan of rock and the mexican##2
5. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
6. the german is between the italian and the fan of soul##2
7. the fan of country is the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
