.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-18::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, r&b, techno, funk
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, epic, romance, sports
4 different pets are kept: cat, hedgehog, horse, mouse
1. the person watching romance movies is the fan of r&b##1
2. the fan of d&b is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
3. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the fan of techno##1
4. the fan of d&b is between the person watching romance movies and the person watching disaster movies##2
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the fan of funk##1
6. the owner of the mouse is between the fan of r&b and the owner of the cat##2
7. the person watching sports movies is the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Music-Genre      | techno | d&b | r&b     | funk   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | sports        | romance  | epic  |
| Pet           | cat      | mouse         | hedgehog | horse |

