2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who growsaconite##1
3. the dancer is on the far left##1
4. the person who growsazalea is the librarian##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person who growsazalea##1
6. the person who growsdaisy is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person who growsazalea##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | dancer        | librarian  | journalist | freelancer   |
| Sport       | weightlifting | ice-hockey | surfing    | snowboarding |
| Flower   | aconite        | azalea     | daisy       | begonia      |

